txt.en: Help to further reinforce the stronghold at Tírith Rhaw by collecting materials to reinforce the gate. You will find all you need throughout the Ettenmoors.
'We need lashing, wood, and iron. You can find these all throughout the Ettenmoors. Please, be swift.'
With Tírith Rhaw captured and the gate built, you are asked to turn your attention to upgrading the gate for greater defence.

'We will hold this tower, though the effort will not be easy. You have done well to help construct the gate here at Tírith Rhaw, but we must reinforce the gate.\n\n'Make your way back into the wilds of the Ettenmoors, collect the wood and iron we need to reinforce the gate here.'
Return to Haliggyr at Tiríth Rhaw
'Yes, this delivery will help us to strengthen the gate below. You are to be commended for your further assistance to us in this war effort in the Ettenmoors.'
Defence: Reinforce the Gate of Tírith Rhaw
